com.akvelon.server.service.api

Interface CultureService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Service<java.lang.String,Culture>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CultureServiceImpl

    public interface CultureService
extends Service<java.lang.String,Culture>
    Standard services operations with Culture objects through CultureDAO objects. The user of this interface can create, read, update, delete domain objects from the database through CultureDAO objects.
